---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import CallToAction from '~/components/widgets/CallToAction.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'About — Aithergy',
  ignoreTitleTemplate: true,
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>

  <!-- HERO ********************************************************* -->

  <section class="relative w-full overflow-hidden min-h-[650px] lg:min-h-[750px]">
    <!-- Light abstract energy-flow background -->
    <div 
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full bg-cover bg-center opacity-90"
      style="background-image: url('/images/about-hero.png');"
    ></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col justify-center h-full px-6 lg:px-12 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-6">
        Aithergy is where AI, energy systems and human performance meet.
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 max-w-2xl">
        Founded by Rohit, Aithergy blends systems thinking, optimisation and modern AI to help founders, operators 
        and energy innovators build clarity, momentum and intelligent solutions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ORIGIN STORY ************************************************* -->

  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-6">The origin</h2>

      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-4">
        Aithergy began with a simple idea: the systems we build — in business, in energy, in our own lives — can be 
        made dramatically more intelligent with the right combination of clarity, structure and AI‑driven insight.
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-4">
        After years of working across technology, optimisation and wellness, I saw the same pattern everywhere: 
        people and organisations were operating with unnecessary friction. Too much noise. Too little clarity. 
        Too many decisions made without the right models.
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
        Aithergy was created to solve that — by bringing together AI, systems thinking and human performance into 
        one coherent approach.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE BELIEVE ********************************************** -->

  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-blue-50/40 dark:bg-transparent">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-6">What we believe</h2>

      <ul class="space-y-6 text-lg text-slate-600">
        <li><strong>Clarity beats complexity.</strong> Most problems are solvable once the noise is removed.</li>
        <li><strong>Systems create outcomes.</strong> Whether in business or energy, structure determines performance.</li>
        <li><strong>AI is a multiplier.</strong> When used intentionally, it amplifies human capability — not replaces it.</li>
        <li><strong>Energy matters.</strong> Human energy. Organisational energy. Renewable energy. It all flows.</li>
        <li><strong>Intelligent design wins.</strong> The future belongs to those who build with intention and insight.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE DO *************************************************** -->

  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="container max-w-5xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-10">What we do</h2>

      <div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-3">

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">AI Strategy</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            Helping founders and operators design intelligent workflows, tools and decision systems that reduce 
            friction and increase clarity.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Systems Thinking</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            Mapping constraints, leverage points and flows to build structures that scale with intention and 
            stability.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Energy Optimisation</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            Using AI‑based optimisation to reduce curtailment, improve utilisation and unlock new value from 
            renewable energy systems.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOUNDER SECTION ********************************************** -->

  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-blue-50/40 dark:bg-transparent">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-6">About Rohit</h2>

      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-4">
        I’ve always been fascinated by systems — how they work, where they break, and how they can be made more 
        intelligent. My background spans AI, optimisation, wellness and energy, and Aithergy is the synthesis of 
        those worlds.
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-4">
        I work with founders, operators and energy innovators who want to build with clarity, reduce friction and 
        design systems that actually support the outcomes they care about.
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
        Whether it’s a founder’s operating system, an AI workflow or a large‑scale energy optimisation model — 
        the goal is always the same: create intelligent flow.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA *********************************************************** -->

  <CallToAction
    actions={[
      {
        variant: 'primary',
        text: 'Get in touch',
        href: 'mailto:info@aithergy.com',
      },
    ]}
  >
    <Fragment slot="title">
      Let’s build intelligently.
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="subtitle">
      If you’re exploring AI, systems design or energy optimisation — I’d love to hear from you.
    </Fragment>
  </CallToAction>

</Layout>
